
<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Final Term end mail</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:300,400,500,700" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Poppins' , sans-serif; font-size:14px;color:#302c2b; line-height:2;">
    <div class="rt-tb-scrl">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p>Dear Sir / Madam,</p>
            This is with reference to the reminder emails sent, 1st reminder on <b>@Model.Reminder1</b> followed by 2nd reminder on <b>@Model.Reminder2</b> regarding the term extension of the project staff as per the details given below:
            <table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" style="margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 10px;text-align:left;width:50%;">
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;">
                        Appointment details
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Project staff name
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        @Model.PersonName
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Employeeid
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        @Model.EmployeeNum
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Project staff designation
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        @Model.DesignationName
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Appointed in the project number
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        @Model.ProjectNumber
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Term ended on
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        @Model.AppointmentEndDate
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Salary
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        Rs . @Model.BasicPay /- pm
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p>
                Since we have not received any response till date regarding the possible extension or recovery of dues, we are processing the relief of the project staff, assuming that there are "no dues" to be recovered or that no further extension is to be processed.
            </p>
            <p>
                In case if there is a need for extension of the project staff in the same or in any other project, it will be treated as a new contract since final settlement has been made in the present contract.
            </p>

            <p>This is for your information.</p>
            <p>
                For any queries, kindly send an email to
                @if (Model.Apptype == "STE")
                {
                    <a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment4@imail.iitm.ac.in" target="_blank"> icsrrecruitment4@imail.iitm.ac.in</a> <span>/</span> <a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in" target="_blank">icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in</a>
                }
                else
                {
                    <a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment5@imail.iitm.ac.in" target="_blank">icsrrecruitment5@imail.iitm.ac.in</a>
                }
                and we will get back to you at the earliest.
            </p>
            <p>Thanks and Regards,</p>
            <p style="margin-top:0px;">
                @Model.DAName<br>
                Project Recruitment<br>
                Centre for IC&SR<br>
                IIT Madras<br>
                *This is a system generated email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
